{"tid":2492752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"智利研究：科興疫苗有效率67%","createTime":"2021-04-17T10:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T08:19:12.000Z","uid":295230,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e4c748f6b97f3557c9f2d25db0ad47551d157470","tid":2492752,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:52:26.000Z","msg":"智利公布一項在現實生活的大規模研究顯示，中國科興新冠疫苗對預防出現有症狀感染的有效率為67%。<br />\n<br />\n當局根據2月和3月疫苗接種計劃的數據，比較接種1劑疫苗、完成兩劑接種與沒有注射疫苗人士的情況後得出結論，共涉及1050萬人。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，接種疫苗對預防有症狀感染的有效率為67%；對預防住院治療的有效率為85%；防止染疫後死亡的有效率為80%。<br />\n<br />\n智利至今已有760萬人打了至少一劑疫苗，其中500多萬人接種了兩劑，佔目標人口的三分一。<br />\n<br />\n智利取得的疫苗中，86.7%屬科興疫苗，其餘為輝瑞/BioNtech疫苗。根據協議，智利將分三年購買6千萬劑科興疫苗。"},{"pid":"f2145cf10c1c5abcb0ad06411a9b268dbca6857e","tid":2492752,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:52:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586308-20210417.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586308-20210417.htm&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL%2FMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=710e2b2f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586308-20210417.htm&h=77aa0a6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586308-20210417.htm</a>"},{"pid":"9c374f4298fee55f5e170c01d0b0e8fccc11615a","tid":2492752,"uid":260744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:55:46.000Z","msg":"智利確診數跌未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb9bc5f77562386b17d59df030800d76c9db6e2","tid":2492752,"uid":98431,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:56:22.000Z","msg":"又放流料<br />\n<br />\n咩撚野研究阿？咁撚多人打都繼續爆"},{"pid":"f4acc7c0ef4912baa4e6990892b391f52fc5a215","tid":2492752,"uid":122377,"like":6,"dislike":21,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"6cb9bc5f77562386b17d59df030800d76c9db6e2","tid":2492752,"